<p>My research blog runs on <a href="https://jekyllrb.com/">Jekyll</a> for eight years now. I wanted something basic back then, plain vanilla as they say in finance, something that would not expire over the years. Something like TEX?</p>

<p>Now eight years later it still works. The math went out of tune, but I just fixed it as instructed <a href="https://quuxplusone.github.io/blog/2018/08/05/mathjax-in-jekyll/">here</a>.</p>

<p>Happy blogging!</p>
